 same model, and it forgets you between sessions. This is your own private AI instance — it remembers every conversation, creates real files you can download, searches the web, and saves work to your personal workspace. It's not a chatbot. It's a worker."},{q:"Can't I just use ChatGPT Plus and a notes app?",a:"You could. But you'd spend your time copy-pasting context, re-explaining your situation, organizing files yourself, and hoping the AI remembers what you told it. With Heyron, context is automatic — your AI already knows your projects, your preferences, and your history. It picks up right where you left off."},{q:"Do I need to be technical?",a:"No. You talk to it like a person. We handle all the infrastructure. You sign up, name your AI, and start chatting in under 2 minutes."},{q:"Is my data private?",a:"Yes. Your instance is completely isolated on its own server. Your conversations and files don't train any models and aren't shared with anyone. It's just yours."},{q:"What happens after I pay?",a:"We spin up your private AI in about 2 minutes. You name it, start a conversation, and you're off. You also get access to our private Discord community where other members share what they're building."},{q:"Can I cancel?",a:"Anytime. No contracts. You can manage your subscription and export your data at heyron.ai/account."}].map(t=>(0,s.jsxs)("div",{className:"lp-faq-item",children:[(0,s.jsxs)("button",{className:"lp-faq-question",onClick:e,children:[t.q,(0,s.jsx)("svg",{viewBox:"0 0 24 24",fill:"none",stroke:"currentColor",strokeWidth:"2",children:(0,s.jsx)("polyline",{points:"6 9 12 15 18 9"})})]}),(0,s.jsx)("div",{className:"lp-faq-answer",children:(0,s.jsx)("p",{children:t.a})})]},t.q))})]})})}function p(){return(0,s.jsx)(a.Suspense,{children:(0,s.jsx)(c,{})})}e.s(["default",()=>p])}]);